snippet.title: Artovya Trailer
snippet.description:
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2270400/Artovya/
Dive into the bizarre land of Artovya in a thrilling CCG! Master five distinct factions—Fantasy, Alien, Futuristic, Horror, and Interdimensional. Forge your strategy with unique mechanics and thrilling battles across fantastical realms. Unleash your creativity, build your deck, and dominate!
